 3 ‚Äî Techniques for Handling Telemetry</strong></h2>\n<p>Operational excellence and problem-solving toolkit .</p>\n<h3 id=\"chapter-11--optimizing-for-regular-expressions-at-scale\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#chapter-11--optimizing-for-regular-expressions-at-scale\" aria-label=\"chapter 11  optimizing for regular expressions at scale permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Chapter 11 ‚Äî Optimizing for Regular Expressions at Scale</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Regex performance tuning in telemetry pipelines.</li>\n<li>Reducing CPU/memory overhead of pattern matching.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"chapter-12--standardized-logging-and-event-formats\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#chapter-12--standardized-logging-and-event-formats\" aria-label=\"chapter 12  standardized logging and event formats permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Chapter 12 ‚Äî Standardized Logging and Event Formats</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Building structured loggers (JSON, YAML).</li>\n<li>Creating sche